## Scope

This license applies to all files in this repository
unless otherwise noted in a subdirectory README.

If implementation specifications, schemas, or
formal protocol definitions are added to this repository
in the future, those materials may be placed under
separate license terms. Any such exception will be
explicitly noted in the relevant subdirectory.

---

## Priority Note

The following concepts were first named and documented
by Hitoshi Watadani in this repository or in the related
character-identity-protocol repository:

- Persistent Anchor Layer (PAL)
- PAL Reconnected Layer (PRL)
- The four-layer operational control model
  described in this repository

If you build on these concepts or use this terminology
in your own work, appropriate attribution is
requested and appreciated.
